snippet.title: PARANOIA - Liam Hemsworth, Amber Heard - New Media Stew Movie Review
snippet.description:
PARANOIA - Liam Hemsworth, Amber Heard - New Media Stew Movie Review

John Basedow (@JohnBasedow) reviews 'Paranoia,' starring Liam Hemsworth, Harrison Ford, Gary Oldman and Amber Heard, with special guest Chrissy Oakes (@ChrissyOakesTV).

MOVIE DESCRIPTION - PARANOIA
An entry-level employee at a powerful corporation finds himself occupying a corner office, but at a dangerous price: he must spy on his boss's old mentor to secure for him a multi-billion dollar advantage.
Cast: Amber Heard, Harrison Ford, Liam Hemsworth, Gary Oldman
Director: Robert Luketic
